<lb ed="L" n="0039b02"/><cb:div type="note"><entry><form><term rend="no_nor"><g ref="#CB05218">𡎺</g></term></form><cb:def><p xml:id="pL154p0039b0202" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">側六切音纖塞也</note>。</p></cb:def></entry><entry cb:place="inline"><form>賺</form><cb:def><p xml:id="pL154p0039b0210" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">直<term rend="no_nor"><g ref="#CB15656">䧟</g></term>切音詀賣也</note>。</p></cb:def></entry><entry cb:place="inline"><form>喙</form><cb:def><p xml:id="pL154p0039b0218" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">許穢切音<unclear></unclear>以喙而息也</note>。</p></cb:def></entry>
<lb ed="L" n="0039b03"/><entry><form>昳</form><cb:def><p xml:id="pL154p0039b0302" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">杜結切音耋日<term rend="no_nor"><g ref="#CB13265">𣅦</g></term>也言日蹉跌而下謂未時也</note>。</p></cb:def></entry><entry cb:place="inline"><form>晡</form><cb:def><p xml:id="pL154p0039b0321" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">奔模切音逋申時也</note>。</p></cb:def></entry><entry cb:place="inline"><form>皴</form>
<lb ed="L" n="0039b04"/><cb:def><p xml:id="pL154p0039b0401" rend="margin-left:1em"><note place="inline">七倫切音逡皮細起也</note>。</p></cb:def></entry></cb:div></cb:div>
